properties.caption: unl_xihoneys  meet golden gamma line  the rho associate chapter of delta xi nu multicultural sorority, inc. is incredibly excited and proud to announce our newest xi honey! she may be a solo, but that just shows how determined she was to become a sister of dxn! our newest member is one of the strongest girls we have ever met and we are so proud of all the hard work she has put into this process! grisela, welcome to the sweetest sisterhood! we love you!    name: grisela nica diego-mateo  big: jessica alegra zuniga  hometown: omaha, nebraska  grade: sophomore  major and minor: elementary and early childhood education with a minor in music technology  fun fact: im a first generation student and the oldest child out of 7 kids  why dxn?: i fell i love with the motto! i wanted to be apart of an organization that values the importance of multicultural education. i felt welcomed by the ladies and felt a warm spot in my heart. my process was paused due to covid-19 but it didnt stop me from becoming a butterfly!  what are you most looking forward to?: im excited to start building memories with my new sisters and to continue promoting the mission statement our founding mothers established! #dxn #deltaxinu #xihoneys #unl #unlgreek 1d
